summary: Everyone knows what day it is. I am not an exception, and I will also write my story. It was because of the reputation album...
body:
Everyone knows what day it is. I am not an exception, and I will also write my story. It was because of the reputation album that I became a swiftie . I remember how I decided to subscribe to Taylor’s Instagram, and watched her stories every day. She counted some days, showed her microphones, and various costumes. At that time, I did not understand that reputation stadium tour would begin soon. I didn’t wait for the release of this album like all the swiftie . Now this album is my favorite. I did not live this year, I did not know everything. I want to live this, wait for singles, look for crazy tips. It is a pity that with the rep did not work out, for that soon ts7. I just want to say thanks to Taylor for this year, and for this excellent album.

@taylorswift

body:
Happy Birthday Reputation

It’s been 1 year since Reputation

1 year ago today, we were all waiting.

Waiting for Taylor to drop the album that was going make us cry, laugh and dance.

The album that was going to shut the ‘she’s a snake’ haters the hell up

The album where Taylor shared with us how she’s doing better than she ever was

The album where Taylor was more alive than ever

Happy birthday to the beginning of the most beautiful era ever

No, it’s more than beautiful…it’s…

Gorgeous
